commit_message:
node_recover support lb policy(3)

This patch revise node recover action to dump info to action.outputs
which will be used in post_op(...) of lb policy, the struct is:

{
    'recovery': {
        'action': 'recreate/reboot/rebuild',
        'node': ['node_id']
    }
}

